      "date": "2015-07-03 17:45:19.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI'm not against having a client-side sanity check. It might make the most sense to do that in userspace (lfs or llapi) so that there can be a decent message shown to the user instead of only on the console.",
