        "subject": "LU-6738 llite: Sanity check fid in ll_fid2path",
        "message": "LU-6738 llite: Sanity check fid in ll_fid2path\n\nWe currently do not sanity check fids provided from\nlfs fid2path before passing them to lower layers.\n\nThis can lead to an LBUG.\n\nInstead, we should sanity check the FID as soon as possible\nand return an error to userspace.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I111fa7027ee1da3895c31ea2585c023e4c2f5b4b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
